original_title: Loudes 68: The Movement of Hip-Hop and Reggaeton
overview: Released as a companion piece to the 10-track audio collection from the Loudes 68 Presents series, this bonus compilation unleashes some of the hottest hip-hop and reggaeton music on the planet via colorful live footage filmed on location in Santo Domingo, Dominican Republic. Featured hip-hop, reggaeton and bachata artists include Boy ("Una Noche Mas"), P. Blades ("El Coqui") and Los Nandez ("El Mero Mero").
title: Loudes 68: The Movement of Hip-Hop and Reggaeton
